NOTE:
Before running the MT5 Crypto Charts Manager, you need to synchronize your computer clock to time.nist.gov by following instructions in either of the links below - depending on your computer running on Windows or Mac OS:
https://www.windowscentral.com/how-manage-time-servers-windows-10
https://tf.nist.gov/service/pdf/macintosh.pdf

Download Link for MT5 Crypto Charts Manager:
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/16RuUhG2JPZdEJCf2LWns9jUEfE3NS9aF?usp=sharing

Download Link for MT5 Platform:
https://www.metatrader5.com/en/download

1. The demo version of the MT5 Crypto Charts Manager has all the features of the official version but expires within 14 days.

2. The official version of the MT5 Crypto Charts Manager costs US$45 including lifetime updates and support like adding new crypto exchanges besides Binance. For those of you who like to have the source code for your own customizations please contact me for the best offer.
